Oh and as you can see, there was a command that has the effect similar to boot all (actually opens a new window).
Anyways, Two issues.
1) Server randomly will not accept any new connections (I am sure this is a firewall problem) until we restart the server. Existing connections will play out as usual. Why?
2) Player count says 60-70, in reality about 25 (before it started plummeting by glitch number one). Cheat client user's probably stacking that up. Easy fix, but does this have any effect on glitch number one?
Whac
